##PROGRAM 12
classes_held = int(input("Enter the number of classes held: "))
classes_attended = int(input("Enter the number of classes attended: "))

attendance_percentage = (classes_attended / classes_held) * 100

print("Percentage of classes attended:", attendance_percentage)

if attendance_percentage < 75:
    print("Sorry, you are not allowed to sit in the exam.")
else:
    print("Congratulations, you are allowed to sit in the exam.")
    
    
   OUTPUT:
Enter the number of classes held: 60
Enter the number of classes attended: 55
Percentage of classes attended: 91.66666666666666
Congratulations, you are allowed to sit in the exam.
